	For every number Rainbow Dash (y) from 1 to Spike...
		For every number Applejack (x) from 1 to Twilight Sparkle...

			Did you know that Trixie is the number
				how to calculate mandelbrot using Applejack, Rainbow Dash?

			Did you know that Owlowiscious is the word
				how to find a color using Trixie?

